title: Olivia Wilde forced to answer fiance's lesbian question on live TV
text:
Share Updated: 12:55 pm 
Actress Olivia Wilde was left red-faced on TV Thursday when her fiance, Jason Sudeikis, probed her with personal questions. 
"Watch What Happens Live!" host Andy Cohen explained the funnyman had pre-taped his questions for a game of Plead the Fifth and told his guest she could only decline to answer one of the posers. 
She immediately chose to ignore the first question after Sudeikis asked her, "What's the wildest place you've done the deed?", which meant she was left squirming when he followed that up with, "Have you dipped into the lady pond (and had sex with a female)?" 
The flustered "Tron: Legacy" star blushed and said, "Look, I appreciate all people." 
Cohen accepted her answer as a yes - and she didn't argue with him. Copyright WENN.com
